name: My feelings
letter: Have you ever wanted to be a princess? Well I have and I think it would be amazing!

name: Don't ever call me Doll
letter: Guys always want to act cool when I play ball, but I hate it when they call me Doll!

name: OOpsie
letter: One time I met this great bunny, she was a real star, but I made the msitake of calling her Doll. Don't do that!
